002B18r 2  rr rr                .word   BasCmdDef-1             ; $94 DEF
002B1Ar 2  rr rr                .word   BasCmdPoke-1            ; $95 POKE
002B1Cr 2  rr rr                .word   BasCmdPrintW-1          ; $96 PRINT
002B1Er 2  rr rr                .word   BasCmdCont-1            ; $97 CONT
